Well, what a woman really wants still remains a mystery. But we do not need to lose hope. Here are a few things that woman wants in her relationship to make it easy for you!&nbsp;1) To Be lovedEvery woman wants a man who can love her like no one else can. It is not the rubies and diamonds that can woo her, all she wants is your love, care and commitment. Show her your love express your feelings tell her how much you love her. Take her on dates and don t forget to compliment her. Make her feel special and that can work wonders for your relationship.&nbsp;